<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Tavern</td></tr>
<tr id="L1"><td><a href="#L1">1</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: On an average industrial planet, in an average slightly seedy bar, is the usual mix of aliens. A scruffy, casually dressed O'Brien is leaning on the bar listening to the conversation over at a table. The Bolian bartender is being discreetly deaf.</td></tr>

<tr id="L2"><td><a href="#L2">2</a></td><td>FLITH:  (non-human) Raimus isn't going to be happy about this.</td></tr>

